        "creation_date": 1410291142,
        "body": "<p>You can put the thread to sleep once you've inserted your specified number of records. <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>        int recordsPerSecond = 100;\n        int totalRecords = 1000;\n        long sleepTime = 900; // in milis (Assuming that 100 mili seconds lapsed in inserting 100 rows)\n\n        for(int i=1; i&lt;=totalRecords; i++){\n\n            if(i%recordsPerSecond==0)\n                Thread.sleep(sleepTime);\n\n            DAO.insert();\n        }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
        "answer_id": 25752227,
        "question_id": 25749978
    }],
